import React, { useRef } from 'react'
import * as rb from 'react-bootstrap'

function Table(props){
    return(
        <rb.Table striped bordered hover>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>User ID</th>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Place At</th>
                    <th>Date and Time</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {props.tableprops}
            </tbody>
        </rb.Table>
    )
}

export default Table
